did.unittitle: Jonathan Edwards College, Yale University, student records

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of student records maintained by the dean of Jonathan Edwards College, Yale University.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-H-1 (YRG 13-H-1), Records of the dean of Jonathan Edwards College.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the records is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Jonathan Edwards College, Yale University, Student Records (RU 133). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The records consist of student records maintained by the dean of Jonathan Edwards College, Yale University.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The records are arranged by accession.
